content.headline: JD.com Beats Quarterly Estimates on Lower Prices and Cost Cutting Moves

JD.com reported it achieved record profitability in the third quarter of fiscal 2023, with earnings per share (EPS) of 6.70 Chinese yuan ($0.92).
